0Daniels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20comes%20next%3F%20Delays%2C%20delays%2C%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-judge-juan-merchan-manhattan-mental-health-court-wednesday-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Juan%20Merchan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20set%20Trump's%20sentencing%20hearing%20for%20July%2011%20at%2011%20a.m.%20ET.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20hearing%2C%20Trump%20could%20face%20up%20to%20a%20four-year%20prison%20sentence%20for%20each%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20don't%20expect%20Trump%20to%20face%20any%20of%20those%20consequences%20before%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20likely%20be%20months%2C%20maybe%20even%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20before%20the%20former%20president%20needs%20to%20address%20them%2C%20Alex%20Reinert%2C%20a%20criminal%20and%20constitutional%20law%20expert%20from%20Cardozo%20School%20of%20Law%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20can%20expect%20months%2C%20a%20year%2C%20more%20than%20a%20year%20of%20potential%20delays%2C%26quot%3B%20Reinert%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20predict%20at%20the%20outset%2C%20but%20it's%20going%20to%20take%20some%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20reason%20for%20delays%20is%20because%20Trump's%20defense%20team%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20appeal%20the%20jury's%20decision.%20And%20there's%20a%20number%20of%20reasons%20they%20can%20seek%20to%20fight%20the%20verdict%2C%20Reinert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attorneys%20can%20raise%20issues%20with%20the%20jury%20instructions%20that%20were%20given%20by%20Justice%20Merchan%2C%20evidentiary%20issues%2C%20or%20even%20challenge%20whether%20the%20Manhattan%20District%20Attorney's%20office%20attempted%20to%20use%20New%20York%20state%20law%20to%20prosecute%20a%20federal%20campaign%20violation%2C%20Reinert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20any%20of%20these%20arguments%20will%20ultimately%20have%20merit%2C%20but%20I%20think%20these%20are%20all%20potential%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20appeal%2C%20which%20can%20come%20after%20Trump's%20sentencing%2C%20Reinert%20said%20it's%20almost%20certain%20that%20any%20sentence%20will%20be%20stayed%20pending%20the%20appeal%2C%20meaning%20Trump%20won't%20have%20to%20face%20the%20consequences%20until%20the%20appeal%20is%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReinert%20added%20that%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20people%20who%20are%20sitting%20in%20prison%20today%20as%20they%20wait%20on%20the%20status%20of%20their%20appeal%20but%20that's%20highly%20unlikely%20to%20happen%20given%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20crime%20and%20who%20the%20defendant%20is%3A%20a%20former%20and%20running%20president.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20be%20shocked%20if%20that%20happens%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Reinert%20said.%20%26quot%3BShocked%20because%20of%20who%20the%20defendant%20is%2C%20and%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20tendency%20to%20treat%20crimes%20like%20this%20differently%20than%20crimes%20of%20violence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-sentencing-date-july-hush-money-trial-conviction-consequences-2024-5-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717107902000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6658f4aed0b8e1c832ca8d80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-sentencing-date-july-hush-money-trial-conviction-consequences-2024-5-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20sentencing%20date%20is%20set%20for%20July%2011%20after%20his%20hush-money%20trial%20conviction%2C%20but%20appealing%20the%20verdict%20will%20delay%20consequences%2C%20legal%20experts%20say%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-sentenci