%20era%20of%20ChatGPT-powered%20propaganda%20is%20upon%20us%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20smartphone%20displaying%20ChatGPT%20with%20the%20OpenAI%20logo%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656ddd5e0ec98e92f74b9466%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20says%20it's%20already%20shut%20down%20influence%20campaigns%20that%20were%20using%20its%20products.%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Raa%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20said%20it%20disrupted%20five%20covert%20influence%20operations%20in%20the%20last%20three%20months.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGroups%20in%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%20Iran%2C%20and%20Israel%20used%20its%20products%2C%20OpenAI%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20buzzy%20AI%20firm%20has%20previously%20pushed%20back%20on%20safety%20concerns%20around%20its%20tools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20Iran%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20others%20are%20using%20OpenAI%20tools%20for%20covert%20influence%20operations%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Fdisrupting-deceptive-uses-of-AI-by-covert-influence-operations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20blog%20post%20on%20Thursday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20OpenAI%20said%20it's%20been%20quick%20to%20react%2C%20disrupting%20five%20operations%20in%20the%20last%20three%20months%20that%20had%20tried%20to%20manipulate%20public%20opinion%20and%20sway%20political%20outcomes%20through%20deception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20operations%20OpenAI%20shut%20down%20harnessed%20AI%20to%20generate%20comments%20and%20articles%20in%20different%20languages%2C%20make%20up%20names%20and%20bios%20for%20fake%20social%20media%20accounts%2C%20debug%20code%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20said%20it%20thwarted%20two%20operations%20in%20Russia%2C%20one%20in%20China%2C%20one%20in%20Iran%2C%20and%20one%20by%20a%20commercial%20company%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20campaigns%20involved%20%26quot%3BRussia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20Indian%20elections%2C%20politics%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20criticisms%20of%20the%20Chinese%20government%20by%20Chinese%20dissidents%20and%20foreign%20governments%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20wrote%20in%20its%20blog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20the%20campaigns%20didn't%20rely%20only%20on%20AI%20tools%2C%20but%20also%20used%20human%20operators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%20Some%20of%20the%20actors%20used%20AI%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20their%20campaigns%2C%20like%20producing%20text%20with%20fewer%20errors%2C%20while%20others%20used%20AI%20to%20increase%20their%20output%2C%20like%20generating%20larger%20volumes%20of%20fake%20comments%20on%20social%20media%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20OpenAI%20said%20the%20operation%20in%20Israel%20used%20AI%20to%20produce%20short%20texts%20about%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20post%20them%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20then%20manufacture%20AI-generated%20replies%20and%20comments%20on%20those%20posts%20from%20fake%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20OpenAI%20noted%2C%20none%20of%20the%20campaigns%20had%20any%20meaningful%20engagement%20from%20actual%20humans%2C%20and%20their%20use%20of%20AI%20did%20not%20help%20them%20increase%20their%20audience%20or%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20said%20its%20own%20AI%20helped%20track%20the%20bad%20actors%20down.%20In%20its%20blog%20post%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20partnered%20with%20businesses%20and%20government%20organizations%20on%20the%20investigations%2C%20which%20were%20fueled%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investigations%20%26quot%3Btook%20days%2C%20rather%20than%20weeks%20or%20months%2C%20thanks%20to%20our%20tooling%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20its%20AI%20products%20also%20have%20built-in%20safety%20defenses%20that%20helped%20reduce%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20bad%20actors%20can%20misuse%20them.%20In%20multiple%20cases%2C%20OpenAI's%20tools%20refused%20to%20produce%20the%20images%20and%20texts%20the%20actors%20had%20requested%2C%20the%20company%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20continues%20to%20flex%20its%20commitment%20to%20safety%20and%20transparency%2C%20but%20not%20everyone%20is%20buying%20it.%20Some%20have%20argued%2C%20including%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20himself%2C%20that%20highly%20advanced%20AI%20could%20pose%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStuart%20Russell%2C%20a%20leading%20AI%20researcher%20and%20a%20pioneer%20of%20the%20technology%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-glory-days-ending-problems-chatgpt-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20thinks%20Altman%20is%20building%20out%20technology%20before%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20make%20it%20safe%20%E2%80%94%20and%20called%20that%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20unacceptable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20why%20most%20of%20the%20safety%20people%20at%20OpenAI%20have%20left%2C%26quot%3B%20Russell%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-powered-propaganda-russia-china-iran-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717106941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656dde827a3c8094d5d91912%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-powered-propaganda-russia-china-iran-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20said%20it's%20been%20quick%20to%20react%2C%20disrupting%20five%20covert%20influence%20operations%20using%20its%20tools%20in%20the%20last%20three%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Geoff%20Weiss%2CGrace%20Eliza%20Goodwin)%2