20payment%20was%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20crime%20to%20prevent%20voters%20from%20knowing%20about%20Trump's%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20defense%20attorneys%20had%20countered%20that%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20influence%20an%20election%26quot%3B%20was%20simply%20%26quot%3Bdemocracy%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20former%20president%20did%20nothing%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Campaigning%20in%20courthouse%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20has%20distracted%20Trump%20from%20his%20campaign%20to%20unseat%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20milked%20the%20media%20attention%20throughout%2C%20with%20daily%20speeches%20in%20front%20of%20the%20cameras%20outside%20the%20courtroom%20in%20which%20he%20complained%20about%20being%20a%20political%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20after%20teasing%20the%20prospect%20for%20weeks%2C%20Trump%20--%20who%20denied%20ever%20having%20sex%20with%20Daniels%20at%20a%202006%20celebrity%20golf%20tournament%20--%20opted%20not%20to%20testify.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeith%20Gaddie%2C%20a%20political%20analyst%20and%20professor%20at%20Texas%20Christian%20University%2C%20said%20the%20political%20impact%20of%20the%20shocking%20events%20has%20yet%20to%20be%20determined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20probably%20doesn't%20move%20a%20lot%20of%20votes%2C%20but%20in%20particular%20states%20with%20particular%20swing%20votes%2C%20it%20could%20matter%20around%20the%20margins.%20So%20in%20particularly%20tight%20races%2C%20it%20can%20tip%20things%20back%20from%20one%20direction%20to%20the%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Republican%2C%20who%20made%20his%20name%20as%20a%20brash%20real%20estate%20mogul%20before%20a%20stunning%20ascent%20to%20the%20nation's%20highest%20office%20in%20the%202016%20election%2C%20now%20faces%20prison%20or%2C%20more%20likely%2C%20probation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20he%20could%20face%20up%20to%20four%20years%20in%20jail%20for%20each%20cou