ts%20after%20visiting%20Mundra%20Port%2C%20and%20Khavda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHad%20a%20fantastic%20meeting%20with%20Mr%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20Chairman%20of%20Adani%20group.%20Deeply%20grateful%20for%20his%20warm%20friendship%20and%20his%20commitment%20to%20strengthening%20the%20special%20partnership%20between%20Japan%20and%20India.%20Eagerly%20looking%20forward%20to%20working%20together%20into%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Ambassador%20Suzuki%20said%20in%20his%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHad%20a%20fantastic%20meeting%20with%20Mr.%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20Chairman%20of%20Adani%20group.%20Deeply%20grateful%20for%20his%20warm%20friendship%2C%20and%20his%20commitment%20to%20strengthening%20the%20special%20partnership%20between%20%F0%9F%87%AF%F0%9F%87%B5%26amp%3B%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3!%3Cbr%3E%5CnEagerly%20looking%20forward%20to%20working%20together%20into%20the%20future!!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F8ShP5jMw77%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F8ShP5jMw77%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Hiroshi%20Suzuki%2C%20Ambassador%20of%20Japan%20(%40HiroSuzukiAmbJP)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHiroSuzukiAmbJP%2Fstatus%2F1796173401633038658%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2030%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapanese%20ambassador%20expressed%20gratitude%20for%20the%20commitment%20shown%20by%20Adani%20to%20enhance%20the%20partnership%20between%20Japan%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20Adani%20Group%20chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%20posted%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20to%20convey%20his%20insights%20following%20his%20meeting%20with%20Japanese%20Ambassador%20Hiroshi%20Suzuki.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHad%20a%20very%20engaging%20discussion%20with%20Amb%20Hiroshi%20Suzuki%20of%20Japan.%20We%20are%20grateful%20for%20his%20visit%20to%20our%20Mundra%20Port%20and%20to%20Khavda%20where%20we%20are%20building%20the%20world's%20largest%20Hybrid%20Renewable%20Energy%20Park%20of%2030%20GW%20capacity.%20The%20Ambassador's%20appreciation%20for%20India's%20culture%2C%20the%20value%20he%20places%20on%20our%20partnership%20and%20his%20tremendous%20support%20for%20India%20are%20truly%20inspiring%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20said%20in%20his%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0The%20coal-to-port%20company%20is%20building%20the%20world's%20largest%20Hybrid%20Renewable%20Energy%20Park%20with%2030%20GW%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20being%20developed%20by%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Limited.%20It%20will%20be%20the%20largest%20power%20plant%20on%20the%20earth%20after%20its%20completion.%20It%20covers%20an%20area%20of%20538%20sq%20km%20on%20arid%20ground%20in%20Khavda%2C%20Kutch%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20company%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20area%20is%20nearly%20as%20big%20as%20Mumbai%20and%20five%20times%20larger%20than%20Paris.%20On%20February%2014%2C%202024%2C%20551%20MW%20of%20solar%20energy%20was%20transferred%20from%20the%20project%20to%20the%20national%20grid%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Limited%20will%20invest%20roughly%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20crore%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visit%20by%20Ambassador%20Suzuki%20to%20the%20Khavda%20project%20site%20and%20the%20Mundra%20Port%20demonstrates%20Japan's%20interest%20in%20and%20support%20for%20India's%20renewable%20energy%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20has%20been%20actively%20funding%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20the%20country%2C%20among%20them%20the%20Mumbai-Ahmedabad%20High-Speed%20Rail%20Project%20(IV)%2C%20The%20Dhubri-Phulbari%20bridge%2C%20Phulbari-Goeragre%20section%20of%20NH%20127B%2C%20Chennai%20Peripheral%20Ring%20Road%2C%20and%20Dedicated%20Freight%20Corridor%20Project%20are%20some%20of%20the%20major%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20e