%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110570627.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20jury%20in%20Donald%20Trump's%20hush%20money%20trial%20deliberated%20after%20hearing%20testimony.%20Details%20included%20American%20Media%20Inc.'s%20payment%20to%20Karen%20McDougal%2C%20the%20National%20Enquirer's%20involvement%2C%20and%20events%20surrounding%20the%20October%202016%20agreement%20with%20Michael%20Cohen.%20Trump%20is%20charged%20with%2034%20counts%20of%20falsifying%20business%20records%20at%20his%20company%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20scheme%20to%20hide%20potentially%20embarrassing%20stories%20about%20him%20during%20his%202016%20presidential%20election%20campaign.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjury-in-trump-hush-money-trial-resumes-deliberations-after-rehearing-instructions-testimony%2Farticleshow%2F110570627.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjury-in-trump-hush-money-trial-resumes-deliberations-after-rehearing-instructions-testimony%2Famp_articleshow%2F110570627.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjury-in-trump-hush-money-trial-resumes-deliberations-after-rehearing-instructions-testimony%2Famp_articleshow%2F110570627.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGoes%20Against%20Our%20Territorial%20Integrity%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20On%20China-Pak%20Infra%20Project%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReiterating%20India's%20stance%20on%20Pakistan-occupied%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(PoJK)%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20official%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20stated%20that%20the%20whole%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Ladakh%20are%20integral%20part%20of%20India.%20He%20stated%20that%20India%20is%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20(CPEC)%20as%20it%20goes%20against%20New%20Delhi's%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20query%20on%20reports%20of%20increased%20cooperation%20between%20Pakistan%20and%20China%20during%20the%20weekly%20media%20briefing%2C%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20PoK%2C%20we%20are%20very%20consistent%20in%20our%20position.%20We%20want%20to%20tell%20you%2C%20the%20whole%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20union%20territories%2C%20they%20are%20part%20of%20India%2C%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20India.%20They%20were%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20India.%20They%20are%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20India%20and%20they%20will%20remain%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20position%20on%20CPEC%20also%20is%20well%20known%20to%20you.%20We%20are%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20it.%20We%20are%20against%20it.%20It%20goes%20against%20our%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20sovereignty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaiswal's%20statement%20comes%20after%20Pakistan%20and%20China%20agreed%20to%20advance%20their%20joint%20project%20CPEC%20and%20backed%20finalising%20the%20modalities%20for%20third-party%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20press%20stakeout%2C%20Pakistan's%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Ishaq%20Dar%20and%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Wang%20Yi%20expressed%20satisfaction%20over%20the%20steady%20pace%20of%20CPEC%20and%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Bfurther%20upgrade%20and%20expand%20this%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20Pakistan-based%20Geo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20after%20co-chairing%20the%20fifth%20Pakistan-China%20Foreign%20Ministers'%20Strategic%20Dialogue%2C%20spoke%20about%20their%20in-depth%20discussion%20on%20the%20multiple%20facets%20of%20their%20bilateral%20relations%20including%20CPEC.%20Ishaq%20Dar%20and%20Wang%20Yi%20expressed%20commitment%20to%20continue%20extending%20support%20to%20each%20other%20on%20issues%20of%20core%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDar%20said%20that%20Pakistan%20and%20China%20would%20pace%20up%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Main%20Line-1%20railway%20line%20project%2C%20Gwadar%20Port%20development%2C%20realignment%20of%20Phase%202%20of%20the%20Karakorum%20Highway%2C%20and%20strengthen%20cooperation%20in%20energy%2C%20agriculture%2C%20mining%2C%20minerals%2C%20information%20technology%2C%20and%20industry%20sectors%2C%20according%20to%20Geo%20News%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20we%20embark%20on%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20CPEC%2C%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20developing%20corridors%20of%20growth%2C%20livelihood%2C%20innovation%2C%20green%20development%2C%20and%20inclusivity%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Geo%20News%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20(CPEC)%20is%20a%20%2450%20billion%20Pakistani%20component%20of%20China's%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI).%20The%203%2C000%20km%20Chinese%20infrastructure%20network%20project%20is%20under%20construction%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20aims%20to%20connect%20Pakistan's%20Gwadar%20and%20Karachi%20ports%20to%20China's%20Xinjiang%20Uygur%20Autonomous%20Region%20by%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20March%2C%20Baloch%20political%20activist%20informed%20the%20United%20Nations%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20about%20the%20ongoing%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20Pakistan's%20Balochistan%20province%2C%20especially%20the%20worsening%20situation%20since%20the%20CPEC%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20making%20an%20intervention%20during%20the%20ongoing%2052nd%20Session%20of%20the%20Council%2C%20Munir%20Mengal%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Baloch%20Voice%20Association%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20in%20Balochistan%2C%20Pakistan%20demands%20immediate%20attention%20due%20to%20the%20systematic%20abuse%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20the%20disregard%20for%20the%20basic%20freedoms%20and%20liberties%20of%20its%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20informed%20the%20Council%20that%20the%20human%20rights%20situation%20in%20Balochistan%20escalated%20after%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20multi-billion%20dollar%20CPEC%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20(CPEC)%20has%20been%20a%20source%20of%20great%20concern%20for%20the%20Baloch%20people.%20This%20multi-billion-dollar%20project%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20eliminate%20the%20Baloch%20people%20from%20their%20land%2C%20loot%20their%20resources%20and%20suppress%20their%20voices.%20The%20Baloch%20people%20are%20facing%20mass%20displacement%2C%20enforced%20disappearances%2C%20and%20military%20operations%2C%20as%20they%20are%20being%20systematically%20neglected%2C%20suppressed%2C%20and%20oppressed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Munir%20Mengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717083180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-10%2F8s13mp88_gwadar_port_cpec_reuters_625x300_26_October_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-in-favour-of-cpec-india-reiterates-its-stance-on-pojk-5780805%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reiterating%20India's%20stance%20on%20Pakistan-occupied%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(PoJK)%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20official%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20stated%20that%20the%20whole%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Ladakh%20are%20integral%20part%20of%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-in-favour-of-cpec-india-reiterates-its-stance-on-pojk-5780805%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-in-favour-of-cpec-india-reiterates-its-stance-on-pojk-5780805%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-in-favour-of-cpec-india-reitera