paigning%20Ends%2C%20PM%20Meditates%20At%20Vivekananda%20Memorial%20In%20Kanniyakumari%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20reached%20Kanniyakumari%20and%20is%20meditating%20at%20the%20Vivekananda%20Rock%20memorial%2C%20where%20he%20will%20remain%20till%20Saturday%20evening.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20meditating%20at%20the%20Dhyan%20Mandapam%2C%20the%20same%20spot%20where%20the%20Hindu%20philosopher-saint%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20had%20meditated%20in%201892%20to%20get%20a%20clear%20vision%20of%20the%20future%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20the%20meeting%20point%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20and%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%20and%20BJP%20leaders%20said%20the%20choice%20of%20Kanniyakumari%20gives%20out%20a%20message%20of%20national%20unity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%202%2C000%20police%20personnel%20have%20been%20posted%20around%20the%20memorial%20to%20ensure%20the%20PM's%20security%2C%20and%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20and%20the%20Navy%20will%20also%20maintain%20vigil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECampaigning%20for%20the%20last%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20ended%20at%205%20pm%20today%20and%20the%20PM%20had%20also%20undertaken%20a%20spiritual%20sojourn%20to%20Kedarnath%20-%20where%20he%20had%20meditated%20in%20a%20cave%20-%20when%20the%20silence%20period%20began%20before%20the%20last%20phase%20of%20the%202019%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM's%20meditation%20has%20also%20sparked%20a%20political%20row.%20The%20Congress%20had%20claimed%20yesterday%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bcircumvent%26quot%3B%20the%20silence%20period%20restrictions%20and%20approached%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20ensure%20that%20visuals%20of%20him%20meditating%20are%20not%20aired%20by%20the%20media%20as%20that%20would%20violate%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct.%20A%20delegation%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20Randeep%20Surjewala%2C%20Abhishek