ice%20facilities%20at%20Cantiague%20Park%20by%20any%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ICC%20said%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20months%20of%20intense%20competitive%20cricket%20under%20night%20lights%2C%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%2C%20sans%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20began%20its%20preparations%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20with%20a%20morning%20training%20session%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%2010.30am%20starts%20for%20all%20its%20preliminary%20games.%20Kohli%20took%20a%20break%20for%20personal%20work%20after%20RCB's%20IPL%20ouster%20and%20in%20all%20likelihood%2C%20he%20will%20join%20the%20squad%20by%20Friday.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20he%20would%20be%20able%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20only%20warm-up%20game%20against%20Bangladesh%20on%20Saturday%20after%20a%20long%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20played%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20matches%20under%20lights%20in%20the%20scorching%20Indian%20summer%2C%20the%20idea%20would%20be%20to%20adjust%20to%20pleasant%20mornings%20where%20temperatures%20will%20hover%20between%2025%20to%2027%20degree%20celsius%20with%20very%20less%20humidity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20white%20kookaburra%20in%20slightly%20windy%20mornings%20could%20be%20a%20challenge%20and%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20that%2C%20the%20severely%20jet-lagged%20bodies%20need%20to%20get%20used%20to%20morning%20conditions.%20And%20this%20is%20why%20the%20support%20staff%2C%20before%20initiating%20the%20skills%20training%20(net%20sessions)%20on%20the%20practice%20pitches%20at%20a%20ground%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20city%2C%20have%20decided%20to%20help%20the%20players%20acclimatise%20with%20the%20conditions%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717082160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fvbodb91_india-t20-world-cup_625x30