0financial%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20airline%20said%20in%20a%20regulatory%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJet%20Airways%2C%20which%20stopped%20flying%20in%20April%202019%20due%20to%20financial%20crunch%2C%20is%20undergoing%20an%20insolvency%20resolution%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20plan%20submitted%20by%20the%20consortium%20of%20Murari%20Lal%20Jalan%20and%20Florian%20Fritsch%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20Mumbai%20bench%20of%20the%20National%20Company%20Law%20Tribunal%20(NCLT)%20in%20June%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20monitoring%20committee%20was%20set%20up%20to%20oversee%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20approved%20plan.%20The%20plan%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20has%20not%20considered%20adopted%20the%20financial%20results%20for%20the%20September%20and%20December%20quarters%20of%20the%20last%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsequently%2C%20the%20audited%20financial%20results%20(standalone)%20of%20the%20company%20for%20the%20quarter%20and%20year%20ended%20March%2031%2C%202024%20also%20could%20not%20be%20considered%20and%20adopted%20by%20the%20monitoring%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20a%20meeting%20will%20be%20convened%20shortly%20to%20consider%20and%20adopt%20the%20aforesaid%20financial%20results%20of%20the%20company.%20Accordingly%2C%20necessary%20intimation%20w.r.t.%20the%20same%20will%20be%20filed%20with%20the%20exchanges%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717078740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fu603cgcg_jet-airways_625x300_14_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjet-airways-says-resolution-plan-at-implementation-stage-q4-res