has%20formally%20concluded.%20As%20per%20the%20existing%20rules%2C%20political%20parties%20are%20required%20to%20enter%20a%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-vs-tmc-lok-sabha-elections-rival-not-enemy-supreme-court-junks-bjp-plea-over-ads-against-tmc-5754743%5C%22%3Esilence%20period%3C%2Fa%3E'%2048%20hours%20before%20voting%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%20126%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Frepresentation-of-the-people-act%5C%22%3ERepresentation%20of%20The%20People%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20provisions%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bprohibition%20of%20public%20meetings%20during%20a%20period%20of%20forty-eight%20hours%20ending%20with%20hour%20fixed%20for%20conclusion%20of%20poll%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20Section%20126A%20places%20restrictions%20on%20the%20publication%20and%20dissemination%20of%20exit%20poll%20results%20before%20voting%20ends.%20The%20logic%20is%20that%20discussion%20about%20such%20surveys%20ahead%20of%20voting%20can%20influence%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Logic%20Behind%20A%20'Silence%20Period'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20'silence%20period'%20allows%20both%20election%20authorities%20and%20political%20parties%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20logistics.%20While%20poll%20officials%20work%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20arrangements%20are%20in%20place%20to%20conduct%20elections%20in%20a%20fair%20and%20peaceful%20fashion%2C%20political%20parties%20and%20their%20cadres%20firm%20up%20arrangements%20to%20get%20out%20the%20vote.%20Away%20from%20the%20hustle%20and%20din%20of%20campaigning%2C%20%C2%A0the%20'silence%20period'%20allows%20the%20voter%2C%20the%20most%20important%20person%20in%20this%20entire%20drill%2C%20time%20to%20cement%20their%20decision%20and%20exercise%20their%20democratic%20right.%20Authorities%20ensure%20that%20no%20public%20meetings%20are%20held%20by%20a%20party%20or%20candidate%20in%20a%20poll-bound%20area%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20campaign%20period%2C%20thus%20providing%20a%20level-playing%20field%20to%20all%20contestants.%20Only%20door-to-door%20campaigning%20is%20allowed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fover-79-000-model-code-violations-reported-through-poll-bodys-c-vigil-app-5335316%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Over%2079%2C000%20Model%20Code%20Violations%20Reported%20through%20Poll%20Body's%20C-Vigil%20App%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20however%2C%20with%20the%20march%20of%20technology%2C%20the%20very%20meaning%20of%20public%20meetings%20has%20changed.%20For%20instance%2C%20while%20parties%20still%20prefer%20physical%20rallies%20to%20demonstrate%20support%2C%20speeches%20and%20campaign%20remarks%20are%20no%20longer%20limited%20geographically.%20TV%20channels%20cover%20public%20rallies%20live%2C%20and%20social%20media%20activity%20can%20disseminate%20a%20message%20far%20and%20beyond%20a%20particular%20rally.%20The%20footprint%20of%20satellite%20pictures%20is%20much%20wider%20than%20the%20actual%20event%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20hard%20for%20the%20chatter%20from%20one%20public%20meeting%20to%20reach%20a%20constituency%20that's%20under%20a%20'silence%20period'.%20This%20is%20best%20seen%20in%20phase-wise%20voting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%20Has%20Moved%20Online%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20half%20of%20the%20country's%20population%20has%20access%20to%20social%20media%20today%2C%20and%20it%20has%20become%20the%20'go-to'%20medium%20for%20everything.%20No%20wonder%20then%20that%20political%20parties%20have%20started%20employing%20social%20media%20experts%20who%20can%20shape%20their%20online%20campaigns%20and%20target%20youth%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-turns-to-influencers-youtubers-to-reach-young-voters-ahead-of-polls-5411309%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0BJP%20Turns%20To%20Influencers%2C%20Youtubers%20To%20Reach%20Young%20Voters%20Ahead%20Of%20Polls%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20summation%2C%20parties%20and%20candidates%20in%20constituencies%20that%20are%20under%20a%20'silence%20zone'%20can%20reach%20voters%20through%20social%20media.%20Links%20can%20be%20shared%20for%20political%20rallies%20being%20held%20outside%20such%20zones.%20Candidates%20can%20deliver%20customised%20messages%20to%20target%20groups%2C%20put%20out%20advertisements%2C%20generate%20automated%20calls%2C%20and%20much%20more.%C2%A0All%20this%20remains%20outside%20the%20realm%20of%20existing%20laws.%20And%20so%2C%20even%20though%20there%20is%20technically%20no%20breach%20in%20real%20terms%2C%20the%20spirit%20behind%20the%20Representation%20of%20The%20People%20Act%20is%20lost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Pressing%20Need%20For%20New%20Rules%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20committee%20headed%20by%20a%20Deputy%20Election%20Commissioner%20submitted%20a%20report%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-election-commission-issues-stern-10-point-warning-to-bjp-and-congress-5720405%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%20observing%20that%20the%20task%20of%20maintaining%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20'silence%20period'%20was%20becoming%20%26quot%3Bincreasingly%20onerous%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20increasing%20influence%20of%20digital%20media%26quot%3B.%20The%20committee%20suggested%20that%20apart%20from%20taking%20a%20legal%20approach%2C%20the%20problem%20required%20proactive%20support%20and%20sustained%20effort%20by%20all%20stakeholders.%20The%20poll%20body%20worked%20with%20social%20media%20and%20digital%20platforms%20to%20develop%20a%20Voluntary%20Code%20Of%20Ethics%2C%20but%20nothing%20much%20happened%20beyond%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20elections%2C%20besides%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-orders-x-to-take-down-select-posts-of-ysr-congress-aap-others-5457533%5C%22%3Easking%20a%20social%20media%20platform%20to%20take%20down%20a%20few%20posts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20wrote%20to%20all%20parties%20about%20using%20the%20medium%20responsibly%20and%20told%20them%20to%20strictly%20avoid%20any%20wrongful%20conduct.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20decades%20ago%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20had%20collaborated%20with%20major%20stakeholders%20to%20counter%20the%20spread%20of%20paid%20news.%20In%20the%20age%20of%20AI%20and%20deepfakes%20today%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20must%20look%20at%20ways%20to%20tackle%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20social%20and%20digital%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(K.V.%20Prasad%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20views%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717070700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Fpm-modi-rally-in-gujarat-pti-650_650x400_71512908406.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-the-myth-of-a-silence-period-when-everyone-is-online-5779040%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parties%20and%20candidates%20in%20constituencies%20that%20are%20under%20a%20'silence%20zone'%20can%20reach%20voters%20through%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-the-myth-of-a-silence-period-when-everyone-is-online-5779040%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kenyan%20climber's%20body%20to%20be%20left%20on%20Everest%20-%20family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717070327000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1754%2Flive%2F34f074d0-1e77-11ef-80aa-699d54c46324.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczkk1081jp5o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2040-year-old%20mountaineer%20fall%20near%20the%20mountain%20peak%20last%20week%20with%20his%20Nepalese%20guide%2C%20who%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1214%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczkk1081jp5o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczkk1081jp5o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fczkk1081jp5o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Land%2C%20Fish%2C%20Fear%3A%20Probe%20Agency%20On%20How%20Shahjahan%20Built%20Sandeshkhali%20Empire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeshkhali%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20the%20man%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20allegations%20that%20evolved%20into%20the%20biggest%20talking%20point%20in%20West%20Bengal%20this%20election%2C%20allegedly%20used%20an%20intricate%20web%20of%20dummy%20traders%2C%20numerous%20properties%20and%20multiple%20bank%20accounts%20to%20turn%20black%20money%20into%20white%2C%20the%20probe%20by%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20agency%20has%20filed%20a%20prosecution%20complaint%20before%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Kolkata%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act.%20%26quot%3BED%20initiated%20investigation%20on%20the%20basis%20of%2013%20FIRs%20registered%20by%20West%20Bengal%20Police%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20IPC%20Act%2C%201860%20and%20Arms%20Act%2C%201959%20against%20Sahajhan%20Sheikh%20and%20others%20on%20the%20allegations%20that%20they%20have%20created%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20terror%20by%20indulging%20in%20organized%20crime%20of%20giving%20threats%20of%20injury%2C%20murder%2C%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20extortion%20etc.%20and%20also%20grabbed%20land%20of%20general%20public%20and%20obtained%20illegal%20monetary%20gains%2Fbenefits%2C%26quot%3B%20ED%20has%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShahjahan's%20Empire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20has%20said%20that%20its%20probe%20found%20that%20Shahjahan%20%26quot%3Bcreated%20a%20criminal%20empire%20revolving%20around%20land%20grabbing%2C%20illegal%20fish%20farming%2Ftrading%2C%20grabbing%20brick%20fields%2C%20cartelization%20of%20contracts%2C%20collection%20of%20illegal%20taxes%2Flevies%2C%20commission%20on%20land%20deals%20etc%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ED%20sources%2C%20the%20former%20Trinamool%20leader%20used%20political%20influence%20and%20armed%20goons%20to%20conduct%20his%20illegal%20businesses%20on%20the%20nondescript%20island%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district.%20Four%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20--%20Shahjahan%2C%20his%20brother%20Alamgir%20and%20the%20strongman's%20aides%20Shib%20Prasad%20Hazra%20and%20Didar%20Boksh%20Molla.%20Statements%20of%20100-odd%20witnesses%20have%20been%20recorded%3B%20these%20include%20local%20farmers%2C%20tribals%2C%20fish%20traders%2C%20landowners%20and%20contractors%20working%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20earlier%20attached%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2027%20crore%20allegedly%20belonging%20to%20Shahjahan%20and%20others.%20Three%20SUVs%20belonging%20to%20the%20strongman%20--%20Mahindra%20Thar%2C%20Jeep%20Compass%20and%20Mahindra%20Scorpio%20--%20have%20been%20seized.%20%26quot%3BOut%20of%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20of%20value%20Rs.261.41%20Crore%20derived%20and%20obtained%20by%20said%20persons%20from%20criminal%20activities%2C%20as%20revealed%20during%20the%20course%20of%20investigation%20conducted%20under%20PMLA%2C%202002%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EED%20sources%20said%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20include%20the%20strongman's%20earnings%20from%20fish%20depots%2C%20rent%20from%20'Shahjahan%20market'%20and%20brick%20kilns.%20They%20also%20include%20government%20tenders%20received%20by%20Alamgir%20and%20Hazra%20due%20to%20Shahjahan's%20political%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Strongman's%20Rise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EED%20sources%20also%20explained%20how%20the%20strongman%2C%20who%20was%20expelled%20by%20Trinamool%20soon%20after%20the%20allegations%20came%20to%20the%20fore%2C%20cleaned%20the%20black%20money%20made%20through%20illegal%20means.%20The%20agency%20has%20said%20in%20its%20chargesheet%20that%20back%20in%202009-2010%2C%20Shahjahan%2C%20then%20a%20CPM%20leader%2C%20grabbed%20fisheries%20of%2060-70%20bighas%20land%20and%20started%20business%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Sk%20Sabina%20Fisheries.%20He%20joined%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%202013%20and%20become%20sub-pradhan%20in%20Agarhati%20gram%20panchayat%20on%20an%20invitation%20from%20then%20local%20Trinamool%20MP%20Haji%20Nurul%20Islam%20and%20with%20the%20backing%20of%20then%20minister%20Jyotipriya%20Mallick%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20one%20hand%2C%20Sk%20Sahajhan%20helped%20people%20by%20offering%20a%20few%20free%20medical%20services%2C%20financial%20aid%2C%20and%20essential%20provisions.%20However%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Sk%20Sahajhan%20employed%20over%20100%20goons%20who%20remained%20close%20to%20him%20and%20his%20residence.%20These%20goons%20would%20intimidate%20and%20extort%20individuals%2C%20compelling%20them%20to%20comply%20with%20Sk%20Sahajhan's%20orders.%20Those%20who%20resisted%20faced%20physical%20violence%20and%20threats%20of%20severe%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bthese%20individuals%20were%20known%20to%20carry%20illegal%20firearms%20and%20were%20not%20hesitant%20to%20use%20excessive%20force%26quot%3B.%C2%A0In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20February%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20suspended%20him%20for%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Money%20Trail%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20money%20trail%20worked%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20says%20Shahjahan%20was%20harvesting%20fish%20on%20grabbed%20land.%20Also%2C%20all%20fish%20vendors%20in%20the%20area%20had%20been%20threatened%20that%20they%20will%20do%20business%20through%20Shahjahan's%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSk%20Sahajhan%20utilised%20his%20terror%20to%20obtain%20huge%20chunks%20of%20lands%20on%20lease%20from%20farmers%2Fvillagers%20in%20the%20name%20of%20his%20associates%20like%20Shib%20Prasad%20Hazra%2C%20Satyajyoti%20Sanyal%20etc.%20Further%2C%20the%20lease%20amount%20was%20paid%20by%20Sk%20Sahajhan%20from%20the%20Proceeds%20of%20Crime%20generated%20by%20him%20through%20grabbed%20land%2C%20threats%2C%20extortion%20etc.%20The%20fishes%20harvested%20on%20such%20grabbed%20and%20leased%20lands%20were%20disguised%20as%20supply%20of%20fish%20by%20said%20dummy%20traders%2C%20dummy%20arots%20to%20SK%20Sabina%20Fish%20Supplier.%20SK%20Sabina%20fish%20Suppliers%20supplied%20these%20fish%20to%20exporters%20and%20accordingly%2C%20funds%20were%20received%20in%20the%20accounts%20of%20SK%20Sabina%20Fish%20Supplier.%20These%20funds%20were%20then%20transferred%20by%20SK%20Sabina%20Fish%20Supplier%20to%20these%20dummy%20traders%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chargesheet%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20coming%20in%20was%20then%20withdrawn%20in%20cash%20and%20handed%20over%20back%20to%20Shahjahan%2C%20ED%20sources%20explained.%20The%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20were%20invested%20in%20buying%20more%20agricultural%20land%20and%20commercial%20buildings.%20These%20properties%20were%20often%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Shahjahan's%20aides%20or%20Sekh%20Sumaiya%20Hafiziya%20Trust%2C%20run%20by%20his%20brother.%20%26quot%3BLands%20have%20been%20grabbed%20by%20Sk%20Sahajhan%20on%20nominal%20rates%20using%20threats%20and%20coercion%20and%20the%20same%20have%20been%20transferred%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Sk%20Sumaiya%20Hafiziya%20Trust%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chargesheet%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Cut%20In%20Every%20Deal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20adds%20that%20Shahjahan%20collected%20on%20the%20purchase%20of%20every%20piece%20of%20land%20in%20the%20area%20and%20also%20used%20his%20influence%20to%20control%20government%20tenders%20in%20the%20area.%20It%20says%20Shahjahan%20and%20his%20aides%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20terror%20and%20political%20clout%2C%20%26quot%3Bmade%20a%20syndication%20in%20government%20tenders%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20nearby%20areas%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20government%20tenders%20at%20Gram%20Panchayat%2C%20Panchayat%20Samiti%20and%20Zila%20Parishad%20level%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20nearby%20areas%20were%20applied%20and%20allotted%20to%20their%20syndicate%20and%20no%20other%20contractor%20was%20allowed%20to%20apply%20for%20tender%20without%20their%20consent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chargesheet%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSk%20Sahajhan%20with%20strong%20political%20backing%20and%20an%20army%20of%20goons%20employed%20various%20means%20to%20establish%20a%20reign%20of%20terror%20and%20illicitly%20acquired%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20by%20commission%20of%20schedule%20offences%20ie.%20threats%2C%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20murder%2C%20extortion%2C%20land%20grabbing%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717067520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F79ve3apo_shahjahan-sheikh_625x300_28_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-shahjahan-sandeshkhali-probe-agency-lists-how-sandeshkhalis-shahjahan-used-fear-to-build-empire-5778866%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sandeshkhali%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20allegedly%20used%20an%20intricate%20web%20of%20dummy%20traders%2C%20numerous%20properties%20and%20multiple%20bank%20accounts%20to%20turn%20black%20money%20into%20white%2C%20the%20probe%20by%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20found.%22%2C%22author%