%20a%20Nature%20Lover%E2%80%99s%20Dream%20Destination%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20her%2010th%20birthday%2C%20Mahima%20Sukhdev%E2%80%99s%20parents%20Vinati%20and%20Pavan%20posed%20a%20very%20important%20question%20to%20her%3A%20How%20would%20you%20like%20to%20celebrate%3F%20They%20had%20imagined%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20coloured%20responses%20%E2%80%94%20think%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20a%20little%20girl%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20fantasies%20%E2%80%94%20and%20weren%E2%80%99t%20prepared%20for%20the%20ask%20to%20be%20a%20trip%20to%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Borivali%20National%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325308%2Frare-wildlife-conservation-photos-from-across-the-world-nature-infocus-kalyan-varma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeep%20love%20for%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20back%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vinati%20reminisces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20humoured%20by%20their%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20request%2C%20the%20couple%20went%20ahead%20and%20planned%20the%20nature%20trip.%20That%20day%2C%20Mahima%E2%80%99s%20friends%20returned%20home%20with%20beautiful%20return%20gifts%20%E2%80%94%20books%20that%20spoke%20of%20the%20birds%20and%20fauna%20at%20the%20national%20park.%20As%20Mahima%20grew%20older%2C%20her%20fascination%20for%20the%20outdoors%20only%20deepened.%20And%20whether%20it%20was%20nature%20trails%2C%20hikes%2C%20trips%20to%20safaris%20or%20afternoon%20picnics%2C%20her%20parents%20would%20always%20oblige.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelling%20these%20stories%20gets%20Vinati%20chuckling.%20After%20all%2C%20she%20sees%20them%20as%20jigsaw%20pieces%20that%20played%20a%20role%20in%20fortifying%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20nature.%20She%20says%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20Mahima%E2%80%99s%20passion%20rubbed%20off%20on%20her%2C%20her%20husband%2C%20and%20their%20daughter%20Ashima%2C%20and%20they%20grew%20as%20intrigued%20by%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinati%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20based%20in%20London%2C%20sees%20those%20years%20of%20innocence%20as%20the%20fabric%20that%20wove%20together%20the%20story%20of%20O%E2%80%99Land%20Plantation%20Stays%20%E2%80%94%20a%20120-acre%20estate%20which%20she%20manages.%20Set%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297379%2Fcouple-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20of%20the%20Nilgiris%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20geographic%20salient%20that%20is%20spread%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%2C%20the%20stay%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20responsible%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20ever%20happen%20to%20be%20in%20Coonoor%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20recommend%3A%20Get%20into%20the%20car%2C%20stock%20it%20up%20with%20provisions%20that%20will%20last%20you%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20then%20drive.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20let%20the%20unsealed%20roads%20daunt%20you.%20Look%20for%20company%20in%20the%20spectacular%20scenery%20instead.%20Keep%20driving%20until%20you%20spot%20a%20carpet%20of%20green.%20This%20will%20be%20your%20first%20indication%20of%20having%20arrived%20at%20the%20O%E2%80%99Land%20Plantation%20Stay.%20The%20place%20is%20a%20great%20draw%20for%20bids%2C%20who%20are%20attracted%20by%20the%20glorious%20view%20%E2%80%94%20a%20set%20of%20three%20cottages%20hugged%20by%20a%20verdant%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20Vinati%20and%20Pavan%2C%20the%20brains%20behind%20this%20oasis%20emphasise%2C%20it%20makes%20for%20a%20great%20relaxing%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fcoonoor-homestay-1716369929.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20al