ecided%20to%20make%20his%20own%20brand%20%E2%80%94%20Iceberg%20Organic%20Icecreams%20based%20out%20of%20his%20hometown%20in%20Nellore%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERoad%20to%20home%20and%20entrepreneurship%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Nellore%2C%20Suhas%20moved%20away%20from%20home%20for%20education.%20%E2%80%9CI%20moved%20to%20different%20cities%20for%20my%20senior%20schooling%20and%20graduation.%20I%20had%20spent%20so%20much%20time%20away%20from%20home%20that%20I%20had%20this%20longing%20to%20be%20back%20in%20my%20hometown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20my%20PhD%20in%20pharmacy%2C%20I%20decided%20that%20it%20was%20time%20for%20me%20to%20move%20back%20and%20stay%20closer%20to%20my%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20this%20move%20also%20meant%20that%20I%20had%20to%20look%20for%20different%20avenues%20of%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20come%20from%20a%20humble%20background%20and%20setting%20up%20my%20own%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F190337%2Fprafulla-chandra-ray-father-indian-chemistry-history-science-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epharma%20company%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20outlet%20in%20Nellore%20was%20not%20a%20possibility.%20While%20I%20had%20never%20thought%20actively%20about%20entrepreneurship%2C%20it%20was%20along%20the%20way%20that%20I%20realised%20that%20it%20might%20be%20my%20calling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Suhas%20moved%20back%20home%20in%202013%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20he%20had%20something%20in%20abundance%20%E2%80%94%20access%20to%20pure%20milk.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20big%20cities%2C%20pure%20and%20organic%20milk%20can%20be%20very%20expensive%2C%20but%20here%2C%20I%20could%20buy%20it%20for%20as%20low%20as%20Rs%2055.%20I%20decided%20to%20think%20in%20that%20direction%20and%20it%20dawned%20on%20me%20that%20an%20ice%20crea